{"segment":3,"line_start":55,"line_end":123,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"放着好好的客栈不去睡，却偏偏要睡我的破桌子，你们这些年轻人，我真不知道你们有什么毛病。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":72,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"不是我有毛病，是他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"是他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"他怕我，因为我不是……","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"因为你不是他的情人，是丁喜的。","tone":"大笑","chapter":12,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"丁喜这小子，果然有两手，果然有眼光。","tone":"大笑","chapter":12,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"这是好消息，我们一定要喝两杯庆祝。","tone":"大笑","chapter":12,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"我们少喝点行不行？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"你是不是想喝醋？","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"就算我要吃醋，吃的也是干醋。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":12,"line_start":104,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"那么你就快喝酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"可是今天……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":12,"line_start":108,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"你放心，胡老五一定要到晚上才会来，因为他的孙大哥一定要等到晚上宵夜时才吃烧鸡，而且要吃新鲜的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":110,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"要我们坐在这里等一天，滋味倒真不好受。","tone":"无奈","chapter":12,"line_start":114,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"你也可以放心，我不会让你们干等的，我的酒足够把你们两个人都泡得完全湿透。","tone":"大笑","chapter":12,"line_start":118,"line_end":120}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":124,"line_end":186,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"现在我们就喝酒来庆祝，未免还太早了些。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"因为……因为我虽然对他好，可是……","tone":"无奈","chapter":12,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"可是那小子却总是对你冷冰冰的，有时还故意要气你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":130,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"他就是这样子。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"这你就不懂了，就因为他喜欢你，所以才会故意作出这样子来。我早就说过，这小子是个怪物。","tone":"大笑","chapter":12,"line_start":136,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_hu_lao_wu","text":"难道你已经喝醉了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_hu_lao_wu","text":"是不是孙毅急着要吃烧鸡？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"这是怎么回事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":164,"line_end":164},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"天知道这是怎么回事，他本来就是个怪物，现在……","tone":"苦笑","chapter":12,"line_start":166,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":null,"text":"果然不愧是拼命胡老五，为了朋友，他也肯这么拼命。","tone":"无奈","chapter":12,"line_start":180,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"他既然这么拼命，这纸卷上一定有很重要的消息。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":184,"line_end":184}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":187,"line_end":264,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"这是什么意思？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"这意思就是说，今夜子时，要我们到大宝塔去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"因为那里一定有很重要的事要发生。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":196,"line_end":196},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"那件事说不定就是揭破这秘密的关健。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":198,"line_end":198},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"大宝塔是个地名？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":200,"line_end":200},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"大宝塔是座宝塔。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"在什么地方？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":204,"line_end":204},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"就在山神庙后面。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":206,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"山神庙在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"就在大宝塔前面。","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":210,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你能不能说清楚点？","tone":"焦急","chapter":12,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"不能。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":216,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"因为那地方是个去不得的地方。","tone":"严肃","chapter":12,"line_start":218,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"据说到那里去的人，从来也没有一个人还能活着回来的。","tone":"严肃","chapter":12,"line_start":222,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"那地方难道有鬼？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":12,"line_start":226,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":228,"line_end":228},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你没有去过？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"就因为我没有去过，所以我现在还活着。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":null,"text":"这么样看来，大宝塔本身一定就有很多秘密，所以……","tone":"沉声","chapter":12,"line_start":238,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"所以我们更非去不可。","tone":"坚定","chapter":12,"line_start":240,"line_end":240},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":null,"text":"既然有大宝塔这么样一个地方，我们总能找得到的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"我们现在就找。","tone":"激动","chapter":12,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"现在不能去。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":252,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我们现在就去，若是被饿虎岗的人发现了，岂非打草惊蛇。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":256,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"说得有道理。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":260,"line_end":260},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"难道我们就这么干坐着，等天黑？","tone":"焦急","chapter":12,"line_start":262,"line_end":262},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我也绝不会让你们干坐着的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":12,"line_start":264,"line_end":264}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":265,"line_end":377,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"现在我们是不是该走了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":284,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"谢谢你的酒，也谢谢你的烧鸡和馒头。","tone":"温柔","chapter":12,"line_start":296,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"你决心要去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":300,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"我是非去不可。","tone":"坚定","chapter":12,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"就算明知道去了回不来，你也是非去不可吗？","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"能不能回来并不重要，重要的是，我们能不能去，该不该去？","tone":"微笑","chapter":12,"line_start":306,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"说得好，好极了。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":12,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"看样子你一定也是非去不可的了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":312,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"只要你觉得应该去做的事，你就非去不可？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"其实我并不是很想去，因为我也怕死，怕得很厉害，可是假如不去，以后的日子一定比死还可怕。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":12,"line_start":318,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"好，说得好。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":12,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"我们走吧。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"我们？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":12,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"我若不带路，你们怎么去？","tone":"微笑","chapter":12,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你难道不能告诉我们路，让我们自己去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"不能。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"为什么不能？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"因为我想去。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":336,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你自己刚才还说过，去了就很难活着回来。","tone":"担心","chapter":12,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我说过之后，你们还是要去，你们能去，我为什么不能？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":12,"line_start":340,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"我们去是有理由的。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我也是有理由，我想去看热闹。","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"这理由不够好。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":12,"line_start":348,"line_end":348},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"对我来说，却已足够了。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":350,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"你们还年青，一个正是花一样的年华，前程如锦；一个又正在得意的时候，不但名满天下，而且有钱有势。我呢？我有什么？","tone":"悲伤","chapter":12,"line_start":352,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"我已是个老头子，半截已入了土，我既没有妻子儿女，也没有田地财产，每天晚上都喝得半死不活的，活着又跟死了有什么区别？你们能为朋友去拼命，为江湖道义出力，我为什么不能？","tone":"激动","chapter":12,"line_start":358,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"你们就算没有拿我当朋友，可是我喜欢你们，喜欢小马，喜欢丁喜，所以我也非去不可。","tone":"激动","chapter":12,"line_start":366,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":null,"text":"我们走吧。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":372,"line_end":372},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"我们？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我们的意思，就是我们三个人。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":376,"line_end":376}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":7,"line_start":378,"line_end":516,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你不把门锁上？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"你们连死活都不在乎，我还在乎这么样一个破馒头店？","tone":"大笑","chapter":12,"line_start":386,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"那就是山神庙？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":406,"line_end":406},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"嗯。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":408,"line_end":408},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"大宝塔就在山神庙后面？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":410,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"嗯。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":412,"line_end":412},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"可是我怎么连宝塔的影子都看不见？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":414,"line_end":414},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"那也许只因为你的眼睛不大好。","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":416,"line_end":416},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你的眼睛好，你看见了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":418,"line_end":418},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"嗯。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":422,"line_end":422},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你说这就是大宝塔？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"嗯。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":432,"line_end":432},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"大大小小的宝塔我倒也见过几座，可是这么样一座宝塔……","tone":"惊讶","chapter":12,"line_start":434,"line_end":434},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我并没有说这是一座宝塔。","tone":"淡然","chapter":12,"line_start":436,"line_end":436},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你没有说过？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":438,"line_end":438},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"这根本不是一座宝塔。","tone":"淡然","chapter":12,"line_start":440,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"这究竟是什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":442,"line_end":444},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"是半座宝塔。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":446,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"怎么？宝塔也有半座的？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":12,"line_start":448,"line_end":448},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"烧鸡有半只的，馒头有半个的，宝塔为什么不能有半座的？","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":450,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"烧鸡馒头都有一个的，那只因另外的一半已被人吃下肚子里。","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":454,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"不错。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"另外的一半宝塔呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"倒了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"怎么会倒的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"因为它太高。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":466,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":null,"text":"宝塔跟人一样，人爬得太高，岂非也一样比较容易倒下去？","tone":"淡然","chapter":12,"line_start":468,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"这宝塔本来有十三层的，听说花了七八年的功夫才盖好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":474,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"现在呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":478,"line_end":478},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"上面七层宝塔倒下来的时候，下面正有很多人在拜祭的。","tone":"严肃","chapter":12,"line_start":480,"line_end":482},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"那么宝塔倒下，岂非压死了很多人？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":12,"line_start":484,"line_end":484},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"据说也不太多，只有十三个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"一个人若是死得很冤枉，阴魂总是不散的，所以这十三个人，就是十三条鬼魂。","tone":"淡然","chapter":12,"line_start":490,"line_end":492},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你能不能不要再说了。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":12,"line_start":496,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"能。","tone":"平静","chapter":12,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"那上面怎么会忽然有人了？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":12,"line_start":502,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"你怎么知道那一定是人？","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":504,"line_end":504},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"你答应我不再说的了。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":12,"line_start":506,"line_end":506},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我说了什么？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":12,"line_start":508,"line_end":508},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":null,"text":"不管那是人是鬼，我都要上去看看。","tone":"坚定","chapter":12,"line_start":510,"line_end":512},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"你用不着去看，我保证那一定是人，只不过，人有时候比鬼还可怕。","tone":"沉声","chapter":12,"line_start":514,"line_end":516}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":8,"line_start":517,"line_end":555,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"但是我们若连看都不敢看，又何必来呢？","tone":"犹豫","chapter":12,"line_start":520,"line_end":520},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我们当然要去看看的。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":522,"line_end":522},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"我们三个人一起去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":524,"line_end":524},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"我一个人过去看，你们两个人在这里看。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":526,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"这里有什么好看的？","tone":"焦急","chapter":12,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"你们可以在这里替我把风，假如我失了手，你们至少还可以做我的接应。","tone":"认真","chapter":12,"line_start":530,"line_end":532},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"可是我……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":12,"line_start":534,"line_end":534},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"三个人的目标是不是比一个人大？","tone":"严肃","chapter":12,"line_start":536,"line_end":536},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"你总不至于希望我们三个人同时被发现，一起栽在这里吧？","tone":"严肃","chapter":12,"line_start":540,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"山神庙后面有棵银杏树，这树离宝塔已不远，我们可以躲在那里替你把风。","tone":"陈述","chapter":12,"line_start":546,"line_end":548},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"却不知树上有杏子没有？","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":550,"line_end":550},{"speaker":"char_lao_shan_dong","speaker_name":"老山东","listener":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","text":"你现在想吃杏子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":12,"line_start":552,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_wang_da_xiao_jie","speaker_name":"王大小姐","listener":"char_lao_shan_dong","text":"我不想吃，我只不过想用它来塞住你的嘴。","tone":"调侃","chapter":12,"line_start":554,"line_end":554}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":9,"line_start":556,"line_end":625,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"塔上神秘人","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"很好，你居然准时来了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":12,"line_start":574,"line_end":576},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"塔上神秘人","listener":"char_deng_ding_hou","text":"你既然已来了，为什么还不上来？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":12,"line_start":580,"line_end":580},{"speaker":"char_deng_ding_hou","speaker_name":"邓定侯","listener":null,"text":"我既然已来了，当然要上去的。","tone":"沉声","chapter":12,"line_start":586,"line_end":588}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
